'''Shahid Gangalal National Heart Centre''' (SGNHC) is a hospital which provides cardiac care, diagnostic and treatment procedures in [[Kathmandu]], [[Nepal]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehimalayantimes.com/rssReference.php?headline=Why+was+he+at+Gangalal+heart+centre%3F&NewsID=281749 |title=Why was he at Gangalal heart centre? - Detail News |publisher=The Himalayan Times |date=2011-03-29 |accessdate=2013-11-18}}</ref><ref name="b">[http://bossnepal.com/sahid-gangalal-national-heart-center/] {{dead link|date=November 2013}}</ref> The hospital is named after [[Gangalal Shrestha]].<ref name="b"/>

==Services==
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sgnhc.org.np/service.htm |title=Shahid Gangalal Health Centre |publisher=Sgnhc.org.np |date= |accessdate=2013-11-18}}</ref>
===Cardiac surgery===
*Coronary revascularization
*Valve surgery
*Congenital heart repair
*Aortic aneurysm repair

===Cardiology===
*Non-invasive Cardiology
*Interventional Cardiology

